You have heard of this term - Security Champions or was it Satellites (that sounds weird..)? 
But what are they really? Is it a good idea? How many companies are doing this? 
If you're convinces it needs to be done, how do you manage a Security Champions programme (at scale)? 
What methods and tools exist? 
This presentation is introducing the new OWASP Top 10 Maturity Categories for Security Champions - method and tool.
